inc_short_description: Change Report Full message on HMI
inc_close_notes:
Procedure RP-20 Change Report Tidy Up to avoid "" Warning
1. Align with PRXXuction for downtime to perform backup. 
2. Log in with Admin Access Level and Press OK
3. Go to F1 Help in the VISUAL software and Unlock Desktop
4. NavCGITte to C:\Fette\PRXXukt
5. Copy the file "changeprot.dat" in the format changeprot.dat DD-MMM-YYYY.
6. Now NavCGITte to F4 Protocols in the VISUAL software
7. Open change report
8. Delete all entries for 3 months at the end of the report.
